text: Patrik Wallón (born May 2, 1988 in Skellefteå) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Skellefteå AIK in the Elitserien. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Skellefteå AIK players Category:Swedish ice hockey defencemen
